The following points were considered during the calculations:
Total sugars in the transgenic oilcane hydrolysate and juice contain glucose, xylose, fructose, sucrose, arabinose and cellobiose. Arabinose was not consumed by the yeast strains.
For ethanol yield estimation, the highest ethanol titer was considered, and corresponding sugar consumption.
